OL,3,CWife of TV doctor Michael Mosley
OL,4,Caccepts his British Podcast Award
OL,6,FThe wife of Michael Mosely has
OL,7,Faccepted a prize on his behalf at the
OL,8,FBritish Podcast Awards saying she
OL,9,Fwishes "more than anything" that he
OL,10,Fwas here remind the audience that life
OL,11,Fis short.
OL,13,FThe TV doctor and broadcaster went
OL,14,Fmissing while on holiday in Greece
OL,15,Fwith his wife Dr Clare Bailey Mosley
OL,16,Fon the island on Symi over the summer.
OL,17,FHis body was found a few days later.
