OL,3,CWife of TV doctor Michael Mosley
OL,4,Caccepts his British Podcast Award
OL,6,FMosley was honoured with the Hall of
OL,7,FFame award at the Outernet in London
OL,8,Ffor his BBC Radio 4 podcast Just One
OL,9,FThing.
OL,11,FAs she accepted the award, Dr Clare, a
OL,12,Fwriter and GP, told the audience:
OL,13,F"Firstly, I wish more than anything
OL,14,Fthat Michael was here himself to be
OL,15,Fcollecting this award.
OL,17,F"One of Michael's very special gifts
OL,18,Fwas also having the right words to
OL,19,Fuse; he always knew the right thing to
OL,20,Fsay, so I hope I can do him some
OL,21,Fjustice this evening."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
