OL,3,CWife of TV doctor Michael Mosley
OL,4,Caccepts his British Podcast Award
OL,6,FShe said the prize "would have meant a
OL,7,Fgreat deal to Michael".
OL,9,FDr Clare thanked people for their
OL,10,F"messages, the letters and outpouring
OL,11,Fof love" which has helped and
OL,12,Fcomforted her family.
OL,14,FShe added: "So thank you ` and can I
OL,15,Fremind you all that life can be
OL,16,Fshorter than you ever imagine, and so
OL,17,Fif there's one thing you do today, hug
OL,18,Fyour loved ones, tell them they are
OL,19,Floved, don't ever take time for
OL,20,Fgranted."
