OL,3,CWife of TV doctor Michael Mosley
OL,4,Caccepts his British Podcast Award
OL,6,FMosley was known for popularising the
OL,7,F5:2 diet, a form of intermittent
OL,8,Ffasting, through his book The Fast
OL,9,FDiet, as well as his documentaries on
OL,10,Fthe BBC and the show Trust Me, I'm A
OL,11,FDoctor.
OL,13,FThe BBC honoured the doctor turned
OL,14,Fbroadcaster with a day dedicated to
OL,15,Fhim where presenters and audiences
OL,16,Fwere encouraged to do "just one thing"
OL,17,Fto improve their wellbeing.
